# Everything Calculator ðŸŒŸ

**A cozy web platform where anyone can instantly generate, use, and browse calculators from natural-language prompts.**

---

## About
Everything Calculator lets users create any calculator they need instantly using plain language.  
Whether itâ€™s a **net worth calculator**, **GPA calculator**, or something completely custom, users can generate, use, and save calculators effortlessly.

---

## Features
- Generate calculators from natural-language prompts  
- Interactive calculator UI (inputs, outputs, formulas)  
- Browse a marketplace of user-created calculators  
- Save calculators anonymously or with optional attribution  
- Rate and like calculators  
- Search and filter calculators  
- Copy results or use them on the spot  

---

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React + Vite + Tailwind CSS  
- **AI:** OpenAI (for interpreting calculator prompts)  
- **Math Logic:** math.js or expr-eval  
- **Auth & Database:** Supabase  
- **State / UI:** Zustand + ShadCN/UI  

---

## Future Roadmap
- User accounts & profiles  
- Public sharing & social feed  
- Comments & community interactions  
- Export calculators or embed them in websites  
